{
  "title": "Xây dựng thế giới ảo",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Xây dựng thế giới ảo</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\">Thông tin về các công cụ và kỹ thuật cho môi trường tương tác và thiết kế cấp độ.</p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Building Virtual Worlds\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/2844e618-76bb-4c3e-8e93-4d5eac4cc301?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/2844e618-76bb-4c3e-8e93-4d5eac4cc301?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/2844e618-76bb-4c3e-8e93-4d5eac4cc301?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"10\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"9\"><!----><block-markdown ngh=\"2\"><div class=\"block-markdown\"><p>Cho dù bạn đang tạo một môi trường thời gian thực nhỏ để hiển thị sản phẩm mới nhất của mình hay một cấp độ trò chơi thế giới mở rộng lớn được thiết kế để đắm chìm tối đa, Unreal Engine cung cấp cho bạn các công cụ để tạo ra thế giới tương tác tuyệt đẹp.</p>\n\n<p>Tại đây, bạn sẽ tìm thấy các chủ đề giúp bạn thiết kế và xây dựng môi trường của mình. Tìm hiểu cách xây dựng trình độ của bạn trong trình chỉnh sửa và làm cho nó trở nên sống động với ánh sáng, đạo cụ, tán lá, v.v.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"startingout\">Bắt đầu</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Get up and running with the basics of the Unreal Editor.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:level-designer-quick-start-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Level Designer Quick Start\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/01430b32-6464-453c-93eb-e6680052cb83/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n\n<h2 id=\"contentguides\">Hướng dẫn nội dung</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"How to use the georeferencing plugin to associate locations in a UE4 level map with locations in physical space\" href=\"#unreal-doc:georeferencing-a-level-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Georeferencing a Level\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/fe848e25-95bf-4b7a-973f-20aa6ee13773/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Information on the Hierarchical Level of Detail system in Unreal Engine\" href=\"#unreal-doc:hierarchical-level-of-detail-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Hierarchical Level of Detail\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/9a6f5f1e-117c-4ed2-84a3-f8aa51e07a96/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"How to work with the Landscape system for creating terrain for large, open, outdoor environments.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:landscape-outdoor-terrain-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Landscape Outdoor Terrain\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/b1143077-511b-445c-acdb-e04929e47ff0/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An introduction to the One File Per Actor System and how it can be used in your projects.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:one-file-per-actor-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"One File Per Actor\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/d19e8090-8f61-4c63-b045-cc8db0d824c2/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Information on tools used in the creation of large outdoor environments.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:open-world-tools-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Open World Tools\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/35c7948a-ee1b-4467-a63e-df87fa32e743/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Topics that demonstrate features and tools for lighting scenes.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:lighting-the-environment-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Lighting the Environment\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/6ac87c9a-797e-4019-9f8b-d2267a504b71/lighting_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Landing page for Procedural Content Generation Framework\" href=\"#unreal-doc:procedural-content-generation-framework-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Procedural Content Generation Framework\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/5946d18e-7ad6-4b4c-9426-fd0fbace8a06/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A collection of features, tools, and information about using the water rendering and meshing system.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:water-system-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Water System\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/4c1bfd32-1f64-4fee-982b-70f34007e38b/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An overview of the World Partition system and how to use it in your projects.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:world-partition-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"World Partition\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/751f0064-3932-4985-a5cd-d8ca36c17db9/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An overview of the interface used for the design and construction of game levels and environments.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:level-editor-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Level Editor\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/71d227f9-244b-4770-ba06-e2f16c49ad56/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An introduction to Actor Editor Context, a system for organizing the Actors in your Level\" href=\"#unreal-doc:actor-editor-context-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Actor Editor Context\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/8f089159-d2f0-4ad4-afa9-487e056a7f6b/topic-image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Asynchronously loading and unloading levels during play to decrease memory usage and create seamless worlds.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:level-streaming-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Level Streaming\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/8cfb8801-a38b-484d-ac8d-8a633a87e4c9/streaming_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Landing page for Blueprint Spline and Spline Mesh Components.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:blueprint-splines-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprint Splines\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/2d639a5e-5124-43bd-994e-1e3f1cead916/splines_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n</div></block-markdown><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></blocks-renderer></div><!----></div></article><!----><div class=\"col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block d-print-none\"><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----></main>",
